# API Integration

The application integrates with several backend services for functionality.

## Firebase Integration
- [src/lib/firebase/config.ts](mdc:src/lib/firebase/config.ts) - Firebase configuration
- Used for authentication and database operations

## Supabase Integration
- [src/lib/supabase.ts](mdc:src/lib/supabase.ts) - Supabase client configuration
- Used for database and storage operations

## Stripe Integration
- [src/lib/stripe/](mdc:src/lib/stripe/) - Stripe payment utilities
- Handles payment processing for appraisal services

## API Service Functions
- [src/lib/api/](mdc:src/lib/api/) - API service functions
- Contains functions for interacting with backend services
- May include WordPress REST API integration for fetching user data

## Upload Utilities
- [src/lib/uploadImage.ts](mdc:src/lib/uploadImage.ts) - Image upload utility
- [src/lib/upload/](mdc:src/lib/upload/) - Additional upload utilities
- Uses tus-js-client for chunked uploading
